My Projects

Editor

With the use of RectJs, I have developed an editor for merely HTML and CSS with preview using the React library.

E-Commerce

With the use of RectJs and PHP for the backend, we have developed an e-commerce website with features like rating and Stripe payment method.

Health Card

Developed a web application with my team members for efficient maintenance of health records and analysis of trends in records. We used HTML, CSS, Ajax, PHP, and MySQL for implementation.

Automatic Form Filler

Built OCR model using ResNet and integrated it with Flask.

Virtual Therapist

Image preprocessing and Feature extraction from Speech from RAVDESS dataset using Mel Frequency Coefficients(MFCC) for emotion detection and integrated the model in GUI based in Python

Bus Reservation

This application basically uses a WPF application to make and cancel bus reservations. Passengers have the option of booking a seat in advance and can view the seats that have already been reserved.
